# Business Requirements Document (BRD)

# Project Name

Pre-Disclosure Request Management System

# Version

1.0

# Prepared By

Business Analysis Team

# Purpose

The purpose of this project is to replace the current SharePoint-based Excel submission process used for Pre-Disclosure Requests with a centralized web-based application.

The new system will improve data accuracy, workflow visibility, approval management, auditability, reporting capabilities, and user experience while eliminating manual Excel handling.

---

# Current Process

Currently:

1. User downloads or accesses a predefined Excel template stored in SharePoint.
2. User manually fills request header information.
3. User enters multiple account/customer details within the spreadsheet.
4. User uploads or shares the completed Excel file.
5. Approval is managed through emails and manual follow-up.
6. Tracking request status is difficult.
7. Historical reporting is limited.

---

# Proposed Solution

Develop a web-based Pre-Disclosure Request Management System using:

* Frontend: Vue.js
* Backend: Django REST Framework
* Database: PostgreSQL

The application will:

* Capture request details through online forms.
* Allow entry of multiple account records.
* Route requests through configurable approval workflows.
* Provide real-time status tracking.
* Maintain full audit history.
* Support document attachments.
* Generate reports and exports.

---

# Business Objectives

The system shall:

1. Eliminate Excel-based submissions.
2. Reduce manual approval tracking.
3. Improve approval turnaround time.
4. Improve data quality and validation.
5. Maintain complete audit history.
6. Standardize approval processes globally.
7. Improve visibility of pending approvals.
8. Support future business expansion.

