# Functional Requirements

## FR-001 Create Request

Users shall be able to create a new Pre-Disclosure Request.

### Fields

* Region
* Pre-Disclosure Type
* Product Category
* Supporting Attachments

---

## FR-002 Save Draft

Users shall be able to save requests in Draft status.

---

## FR-003 Edit Draft

Users shall be able to modify draft requests prior to submission.

---

## FR-004 Submit Request

Users shall be able to submit requests for approval.

Upon submission:

* Workflow shall be generated automatically.
* Notification emails shall be sent.

---

## FR-005 Manage Accounts

Users shall be able to add multiple accounts under a request.

Each account shall contain:

* Account Name
* Website URL
* NDA Status
* Disclosure Format
* Disclosure Reason
* Product Information
* Disclosure Date
* Disclosure Location
* Responsible Persons
* Individuals Receiving Disclosure
* Information to be Disclosed
* Retailer Ranking
* Volume Estimation
* Additional Notes

---

## FR-006 Account Validation

System shall validate mandatory fields before submission.

Examples:

* Account Name required
* Disclosure Date required
* NDA Status required

---

## FR-007 Attachment Upload

Users shall be able to upload supporting documents.

Supported formats:

* XLSX
* PDF
* DOCX
* JPG
* PNG

---

## FR-008 Workflow Routing

System shall automatically determine approval workflow based on:

* Region
* Pre-Disclosure Type
* Product Category

---

## FR-009 Approval Types

System shall support:

### Single Approval

One specific approver required.

### Any-One Approval

Any one approver from a defined group.

### All Approval

All assigned approvers must approve.

### Quorum Approval

A configurable number of approvals required.

Example:

2 approvals required from:

* Maru
* Sozo
* Naohiro
* Sammy

---

## FR-010 Approve Request

Approvers shall be able to approve assigned tasks.

---

## FR-011 Reject Request

Approvers shall be able to reject requests.

Mandatory rejection comments required.

---

## FR-012 Workflow Progress Tracking

Users shall be able to view:

* Current approver
* Current level
* Approval history
* Approval comments

---

## FR-013 Email Notifications

System shall send email notifications for:

### Submission

Notify first approver.

### Approval

Notify next approver.

### Rejection

Notify requestor.

### Final Approval

Notify requestor.

---

## FR-014 Audit Trail

System shall record:

* Request creation
* Updates
* Submission
* Approvals
* Rejections
* Comments

---

## FR-015 Search Requests

Users shall search by:

* Request Number
* Region
* Type
* Category
* Status
* Requestor
* Date Range

---

## FR-016 Reporting

System shall provide reports for:

* Pending Requests
* Approved Requests
* Rejected Requests
* Approval Turnaround Time
* Requests by Region
* Requests by Product Category

---

## FR-017 Excel Export

Users shall be able to export request information to Excel.

---

# Workflow Requirements

## Trade Workflow

Approval routing shall follow business-defined Trade workflow.

---

## B2B Workflow

Approval routing shall follow business-defined B2B workflow.

---

## Media Workflow

Approval routing shall follow business-defined Media workflow.

---

## Workflow Configuration

Workflow shall be configurable without code changes.

Administrators shall maintain:

* Approval levels
* Approvers
* Approval types
* Approval quorum

