# Status Definitions

| Status      | Description                     |
| ----------- | ------------------------------- |
| Draft       | Request saved but not submitted |
| Submitted   | Request submitted               |
| In Approval | Under review                    |
| Approved    | Fully approved                  |
| Rejected    | Rejected by approver            |
| Cancelled   | Cancelled by requestor          |

